<function>

access:   public

name: addQuery

param: string, $key

param: string, $val, ''

return: void

</function>

Adds an element to the $this->query array.

* Parameters:

 * string //$key//: The GET variable name to work with.

 * string //$val//: The value to use.

* Returns void

Adds an element to the $this->query array.

If the element already exists, the element is converted to an array
and the value is appended to that array.